   "source": [
    "# 频谱分析示例\n",
    "\n",
    "本示例展示如何生成信号并进行频谱分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy import signal\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置中文显示\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['Arial Unicode MS', 'SimHei']\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置图形大小\n",
    "plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (12, 8)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 生成混合频率信号\n",
    "\n",
    "创建一个包含多个频率成分的信号"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 采样参数\n",
    "fs = 1000  # 采样频率\n",
    "T = 1.0    # 采样时长\n",
    "t = np.linspace(0, T, int(fs * T), endpoint=False)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 生成信号：包含 50Hz、120Hz 和 200Hz 的正弦波\n",
    "signal_50 = 1.0 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * 50 * t)\n",
    "signal_120 = 0.5 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * 120 * t)\n",
    "signal_200 = 0.3 * np.sin(2 * np.pi * 200 * t)\n",
    "noise = 0.1 * np.random.randn(len(t))\n",
    "\n",
    "combined_signal = signal_50 + signal_120 + signal_200 + noise\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制时域信号\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12, 4))\n",
    "plt.plot(t[:500], combined_signal[:500], 'b-', linewidth=1)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('时间 (s)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('幅度')\n",
    "plt.title('混合频率时域信号 (显示前0.5秒)')\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"信号长度: {len(combined_signal)} 个采样点\")\n",
    "print(f\"采样频率: {fs} Hz\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 计算频谱\n",
    "\n",
    "使用 FFT（快速傅里叶变换）计算信号的频谱"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 计算 FFT\n",
    "n = len(combined_signal)\n",
    "fft_result = np.fft.fft(combined_signal)\n",
    "fft_freq = np.fft.fftfreq(n, 1/fs)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 计算幅度谱（取绝对值并归一化）\n",
    "amplitude_spectrum = 2 * np.abs(fft_result) / n\n",
    "\n",
    "# 只取正频率部分\n",
    "positive_freq_idx = fft_freq >= 0\n",
    "fft_freq_positive = fft_freq[positive_freq_idx]\n",
    "amplitude_spectrum_positive = amplitude_spectrum[positive_freq_idx]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制频谱\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))\n",
    "plt.plot(fft_freq_positive, amplitude_spectrum_positive, 'r-', linewidth=1.5)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('频率 (Hz)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('幅度')\n",
    "plt.title('信号的频谱 (FFT)')\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "plt.xlim([0, 300])  # 限制频率范围以便观察主要成分\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 功率谱密度\n",
    "\n",
    "使用 Welch 方法计算功率谱密度"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 使用 Welch 方法计算功率谱密度\n",
    "frequencies, psd = signal.welch(combined_signal, fs, nperseg=256)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制功率谱密度\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))\n",
    "plt.semilogy(frequencies, psd, 'g-', linewidth=1.5)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('频率 (Hz)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('功率谱密度 (dB/Hz)')\n",
    "plt.title('功率谱密度 (Welch 方法)')\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "plt.xlim([0, 300])\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 频谱图\n",
    "\n",
    "如果信号随时间变化，可以使用短时傅里叶变换显示频谱图"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 创建一个频率随时间变化的信号\n",
    "chirp_signal = signal.chirp(t, f0=50, f1=250, t1=T, method='linear')\n",
    "chirp_signal += 0.2 * np.random.randn(len(t))\n",
    "\n",
    "# 计算短时傅里叶变换\n",
    "frequencies, times, Sxx = signal.spectrogram(chirp_signal, fs, nperseg=128)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制频谱图\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))\n",
    "plt.pcolormesh(times, frequencies, 10 * np.log10(Sxx), shading='gouraud', cmap='viridis')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('频率 (Hz)')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('时间 (s)')\n",
    "plt.title('频谱图')\n",
    "plt.colorbar(label='功率谱密度 (dB)')\n",
    "plt.ylim([0, 300])\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 总结\n",
    "\n",
    "本示例展示了：\n",
    "1. 生成包含多个频率成分的信号\n",
    "2. 使用 FFT 进行频谱分析\n",
    "3. 使用 Welch 方法计算功率谱密度\n",
    "4. 使用 STFT 显示频谱图\n",
    "\n",
    "这些方法广泛应用于信号处理、音频分析、振动分析等领域。"
   ]
  }
 ],
